{"tid":226320,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣，潛意識已經記得行返屋企嘅路？","createTime":"2017-05-02T12:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T14:02:28.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"591b1d602e49febc0bff1fb8510cbf4680f1a859","tid":226320,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"行返屋企嘅路人人都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我意思係有時出街食飯 食完飯行返屋企<br />\n我全程都係集中望住部電話 但我可路都唔望一眼就行到返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係好似已經慣晒一條路 連眼尾都唔洗望下就行晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597a935e37e5deb16a34e7d4aeac104f38e60fc0","tid":226320,"uid":50826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:17:12.000Z","msg":"因為你認得路"},{"pid":"815e2655a45ffb5d64f54008efc342b8fcfe173e","tid":226320,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你認得路</blockquote><br />\n個腦認得 所以連望都唔洗望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dbfa39098c76b28ca5929f28a00f9f808f4250","tid":226320,"uid":13512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:02:28.000Z","msg":"睇住俾車撞撚死"}]}